title: ZELDA ROM COLLECTION (463) [w/ Mac Emulators]
description:
Here is my collection of 463 roms for The Legend of Zelda. [2.49 GB]

In addition to every Zelda rom I could find I've added other roms that have Zelda-themed hacks. Some are insanely funny!

I do not claim this to be a complete Zelda collection of everything ever released, only everything a die-hard fan like myself could find.
I hope you enjoy Zelda as much as I do!
